notes.title: How do I create an account?
notes.content: Click the 'Sign Up' button in the top right corner and follow the registration process.

notes.title: Can I reset my password?
notes.content: Yes, you can reset your password by clicking the 'Forgot Password' link in the login form.

notes.title: How do I log in?
notes.content: Click the 'Log In' button in the top right corner and enter your email and password.

notes.title: Can I log out?
notes.content: Yes, you can log out by clicking the 'Log Out' button in the top right corner.

notes.title: How do I create a note?
notes.content: Click the 'Add Note' button in the top right corner and enter the note details.

notes.title: Can I edit a note?
notes.content: Yes, you can edit a note by clicking the 'Edit' button next to the note.

notes.title: How do I delete a note?
notes.content: Click the 'Delete' button next to the note.

notes.title: Can I search for notes?
notes.content: Yes, you can search for notes by typing in the search bar.
